Auto Release	UNKNOWN STEP	2026-06-24T16:13:43.7011708Z               "message": "feat(issue-559): recognition cues as reviewable link data (R341)\n\nLift the meta core's hardcoded natural-language recognition cues out of\ninline Rust literals into data/meta/cue-lexicon.lino. Each cue is now a\nreviewable link grouped into a named cue_set declaring its match mode\n(token / substring / prefix). src/cue_lexicon.rs reads the data once and\nexposes matches()/cues(); the Rust call sites in intent_formalization\n(append_prompt_relevants, looks_arithmetic, looks_like_text_manipulation)\nkeep only the structural glue. Behavior-preserving: the data reproduces\nthe lists it replaced exactly, proven by the grounding/routing tests.",
