Auto Release	UNKNOWN STEP	2026-06-24T16:13:43.7021829Z               "message": "feat(issue-559): proposal-only skill ledger as twelfth meta step (R342)\n\nDistill each request's solution evidence into reusable learning: every\nsatisfied need becomes a proposed CandidateSkill, every blocked need a\nCurriculumItem. Accumulation is proposal-only and gated (tests + benchmark\ndelta), so nothing is ever auto-promoted. Default off mode is behavior-\npreserving (R13); the recipe describes the new stage to keep the meta\nself-improvement loop self-consistent.\n\nMove SolverConfig::from_env body into solver_helpers::config_from_env to\nkeep src/solver.rs under the 1000-line cap.",
